column5: Are house boats available on Lac Suel? If so how do I contact someone with house boats to rent? Thanks

I know of 2 places: White Wing Resort (West Side of Lac Seul) Ear Falls, Ontario Winter Phone: 229-533-7813 whitewingresort.com Lac Seul Floating Lodges (east Side of Lac Seul) Hudson, Ontario Winter Phone: 229-533-7813 (in Georgia)
Both of those phone numbers are the same!!??

Sorry about that. I have changed the Lac Seul Floating Lodge phone number. I know of 2 places: White Wing Resort (West Side of Lac Seul) Ear Falls, Ontario Winter Phone: 229-533-7813 whitewingresort.com Lac Seul Floating Lodges (east Side of Lac Seul) Hudson, Ontario Winter Phone: 807-582-3284
